<% content_for :title do %> - SDK<% end %>
<div class="wl-content-container" id="developer_container">
    <div id="developer_artwork"></div>
    <div id="developer_videocontent" class="wl-inset-shadow-container" style="display:none">
        <div id="developer_videocontent_container"></div>
        <h1>Getting started</h1>
    </div>
    <div id="developer_introduction">
        <h1>Start developing Sakai OAE Widgets:</h1>
        <h2>Design. Develop. Inspire.</h2>
        <p>A 'Widget' is an app which can be used as a 'bolt on' to the installed Sakai Open Academic Environment to add additional functionality, expanding the value of the platform for tutors and students alike.</p>
        <%= link_to "Visit the Widget SDK", "/sdk/developwidget", :class => "wl-button wl-link-button wl-header-button"%>
    </div>
    <hr class="wl-hidden wl-push"/>
    <div id="developer_wheretobegin_container">
        <h1>Where to begin...</h1>
        <div class="wl-widget-item">
            <h1>Developing a Widget</h1>
            <%= image_tag "developer_wgt_icon.png", :alt => "Developing a Widget" %>
            <p>Detailed instructions for developing your own widgets.</p>
            <%= link_to "How to do it", "/sdk/developwidget", :class => "wl-regular-link wl-bold"%>
        </div>
        <div class="wl-widget-item">
            <h1>Examples</h1>
            <%= image_tag "developer_examples_icon.png", :alt => "Examples" %>
            <p>Examples of widgets for various categories.</p>
            <%= link_to "View the examples", "/sdk/designguide/widgetdesigns", :class => "wl-regular-link wl-bold"%>
        </div>
        <div class="wl-widget-item">
            <h1>Widget builder</h1>
            <%= image_tag "developer_widgetbuilder_icon.png", :alt => "Widget builder" %>
            <p>Fill out a simple form and create a skeleton widget framework.</p>
            <%= link_to "Get started", "/sdk/developwidget/widgetbuilder", :class => "wl-regular-link wl-bold"%>
        </div>
        <div class="wl-widget-item last">
            <h1>FAQ</h1>
            <%= image_tag "developer_faq_icon.png", :alt => "FAQ" %>
            <p>The most frequently asked questions answered here.</p>
            <%= link_to "View the questions", "/sdk/faq", :class => "wl-regular-link wl-bold"%>
        </div>
        <div class="developer_threecolumn first">
            <h1>Code best practices</h1>
            <p>Follow these simple few rules and you will be creating your own widgets for others to use on their Sakai platform.</p>
            <%= link_to "View the examples", "/sdk/developwidget/codestyleguide", :class => "wl-regular-link wl-bold"%>
        </div>
        <div class="developer_threecolumn">
            <h1>Design style guide</h1>
            <p>Style your widgets and allow them to fit seamlessly into the Sakai OAE suite of Widgets.</p>
            <%= link_to "Colors, styles... all here", "/sdk/designguide", :class => "wl-regular-link wl-bold"%>
        </div>
        <div class="developer_threecolumn last">
            <h1>UI and API documentation</h1>
            <p>Use build-in JavaScript functionality and learn how to communicate with the server.</p>
            <%= link_to "View documentation", "/sdk/api", :class => "wl-regular-link wl-bold"%>
        </div>
        <hr class="wl-hidden wl-push"/>
    </div>
</div>
